{
  "openapi": "3.1.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "Blog Platform API",
    "description": "\n# Blog Platform RESTful API\n\nWelcome to the Blog Platform API documentation. This API provides access to all blog platform features with world-class design standards.\n\n## Features\n\n- **JWT-based Authentication**: Secure token-based authentication with refresh token support\n- **RESTful Resource Management**: Standard HTTP methods for CRUD operations\n- **Advanced Querying**: Support for pagination, sorting, filtering, and field selection\n- **HATEOAS Links**: Hypermedia links for resource navigation\n- **Rate Limiting**: Configurable rate limits per endpoint\n- **Caching**: Redis-based caching for improved performance\n\n## Authentication\n\nMost endpoints require authentication. Include your JWT token in the Authorization header:\n\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>\n```\n\n## Error Handling\n\nAll errors follow a consistent format:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": false,\n  \"error\": {\n    \"code\": \"ERROR_CODE\",\n    \"message\": \"Human-readable error message\",\n    \"type\": \"400\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Pagination\n\nList endpoints support pagination:\n\n- `page`: Page number (default: 1)\n- `limit`: Items per page (default: 20, max: 100)\n\nResponse includes pagination metadata:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"items\": [...],\n    \"meta\": {\n      \"page\": 1,\n      \"limit\": 20,\n      \"total\": 100,\n      \"total_pages\": 5,\n      \"has_next\": true,\n      \"has_prev\": false\n    }\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## Rate Limiting\n\n- **Anonymous**: 100 requests/minute\n- **Authenticated**: 1000 requests/minute\n\nRate limit headers are included in every response.\n\n## SDK & Libraries\n\nOfficial SDKs:\n- JavaScript/TypeScript: Coming soon\n- Python: Coming soon\n- Rust: See this repository\n\n## Support\n\n- Documentation: https://docs.yourdomain.com\n- GitHub: https://github.com/your-org/blog-api\n- Issues: https://github.com/your-org/blog-api/issues\n        ",
    "contact": {
      "name": "API Support",
      "email": "api@example.com"
    },
    "license": {
      "name": "MIT",
      "url": "https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT"
    },
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "https://api.example.com/v1",
      "description": "Production server"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://staging-api.example.com/v1",
      "description": "Staging server"
    },
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:3000/v1",
      "description": "Development server"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/auth/login": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "auth"
        ],
        "summary": "用户登录",
        "operationId": "login",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/LoginRequest"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "登录成功",
            "headers": {
              "set-cookie": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "string"
                },
                "description": "HTTP-only refresh token cookie"
              }
            },
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AuthResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "邮箱或密码错误"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/logout": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "auth"
        ],
        "summary": "用户登出",
        "operationId": "logout",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "登出成功"
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "未认证"
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "BearerAuth": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/auth/me": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "auth"
        ],
        "summary": "获取当前用户信息",
        "operationId": "me",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "获取用户信息成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/UserInfo"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "未认证"
          }
        },
        "security": [
          {
            "BearerAuth": []
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    "/auth/refresh": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "auth"
        ],
        "summary": "刷新访问令牌",
        "operationId": "refresh",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Token刷新成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {},
                "example": {
                  "access_token": "new_access_token"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "缺少refresh token cookie"
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "无效或过期的refresh token"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/register": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "auth"
        ],
        "summary": "用户注册",
        "operationId": "register",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/RegisterRequest"
              }
            }
          },
          "required": true
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "注册成功",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/AuthResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "输入无效"
          },
          "409": {
            "description": "邮箱或用户名已存在"
          }
        }
      }
    },
